Comment: Not a good move for Black; better to do Nc6 instead.
Black probably wants to do Bb7 with this move.
Moving the knight out of the way
Instead of doing this move to keep the knight safe, it might have been better to do Ne7.
Preparing to move out my bishop.
Black moves out the pawn. If I were in this position, I would have moved it to a6 instead to force me to move the bishop.
